title: VJ Bani’s Super Cute Gym Selfie With Boyfriend Yuvraj Thakur
text:
Swagata Dam Mar . 18 . 2017 
Rumours suggested that VJ Bani had parted ways with her boyfriend Yuvraj Thakur after coming out of the Boss Boss 10 house. But the duo put these rumours to rest and proved there’s no trouble in paradise by posting pictures with each other on social media. I just came across yet another photo of the couple, where they are seen at the gym. After all, both of them are absolute fitness junkies. Check this out. VJ Bani and Yuvraj Thakur | Source: Instagram | 
Cuties.
